Body:
I did Format All + Download option using the latest SPFT and it was successfully burnt the Android Image 8.1 onto the board. So unknowingly doing this, the board lost it's calibration. I tried to calibrate the board using MauiMETA_exe_v9.1724.25.00 tool as per their guidance and the calibration is also successful. So I hope both the calibration and OS also downloaded now to the ROM.

Eventually I tried to start the board, the monitor shows no signal. Looks like board is not booting up, both the red and green lights are ON. Somebody please advise what might be the problem???
